08768355e161c5fe249abcec692","tid":1493724,"uid":3419,"like":47,"dislike":3,"score":44,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T10:54:59.000Z","msg":"intern都想死 咁遲下出嚟做嘢咪想自爆？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nintern先大撚哂喎 <br />\n屌你咪當聽唔到 夠鐘就走人<br />\ncontract一完拍拍蘿柚就走得<br />\n手信唔係應份買俾你㗎喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T10:57:33.000Z","msg":"Thanks巴打，你都講得啱，可能我玻璃心啩<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T11:04:53.000Z","msg":"係呢個社會太病態唔好怪自已<br />\nintern 好處係一兩個月就走，以後唔會再見到佢地，所以唔洗因爲佢地而唔開心<br />\n同埋我諗最重要係睇下係咪呢行既問題/文化(eg 工程) 如果係既話自己會唔會唔適合同想轉？襯未出嚟社會仲有機會探索多啲出路<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e033dc8a595cc8592ec786b246a8d327637ab47","tid":1493724,"uid":257689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c1a962af4da1db38b15ef1bb775824e59d2d2217","tid":1493724,"uid":275587,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T11:01:53.000Z","msg":"我公司三個intern 對佢哋好好 雖然大把手尾汁 不過小朋友係咁㗎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T11:05:22.000Z","msg":"你真係好上司<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，intern跟着你真係好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，有時真係crosscheck咗好多次都錯，自己都唔想<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bdad1975e9347ccbcb38312e113b6a825523a81","tid":1493724,"uid":70008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a52a44dced29e18ee8b7236a2aa80e03af903550","tid":1493724,"uid":257689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T10:50:24.000Z","msg":"返intern成日比人鬧，日日都好痛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，明明都冇做錯嘢，都要比人雞蛋裏挑骨頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" cla